assessment）</li>	<li>咬合不正分类（Classification of malocclusion）</li>	<li>矫治（Orthodontic technique）</li>	<li>正畸治疗风险（Risks of orthodontic treatment）</li>	<li>加多学科治疗（Multidisciplinary care）</li>	<li>科研实践（Research practice）*(3)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>格拉斯哥大学牙医学院开设的研究领域如下：</p><ul>	<li>社区口腔健康（Community Oral Health）</li>	<li>感染与免疫（Infection and Immunity）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>中国申请者学校背景与学术成绩要求：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVp0Lr9Df3Kcdddddd_eEBvW9MbwSLSL0oZ4tp_XgK_LgYb4g3Jegpb4gs2Yy4Ra7mKsOm9xpsvbGru2Q_P' target='_blank'>Chinese institutions and entry requirements </a>(PDF)</li>	<li>牙医学院授课型项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vrjL5VUFG98444444qZplP6qL45LHRKRKPd2a6mZaG_bavJXAHY8yaeSdAWpUALeouyVgu73-DkTSUkUupICtjIstnzMK' target='_blank'>Postgraduate taught degrees</a></li>	<li>牙医学院PhD研究项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2QMwr-KevP7O2AnZEB02TiJkGZhnlhdwcxpd68mvgrk4dyBya64I8FmM1SSgJmOMgdRpbh0BeX9b5piYhUoq5PGRbd9ZJpUWo5fVL9wueU8FoW-cSYaqz2eKCdchBBJQ29VJdmBpQX9' target='_blank'>Research Students &amp; Projects</a></li>	<li>奖学金搜索工具：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrMdLH56-e5XrPC9l4amzeyaY4Ua__lGyRD6rvDXX75H8Sl4DVW-4Wq7shjjqjDwjAqBIePXa_Da4Ch' target='_blank'>Scholarships and funding</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhljakAlE5YtEggggggT8us4OgQPBW45q5q3to85YHhkcUh9l5c2X0fLpHdHsyJh6jG5FSZqFuwxex_x6gMA0qstMQ4Xdfptz7j-' target='_blank'>Endodontics MSc (Dent Sci</a>) University of Glasgow</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nVALEo5iCbvkWoUEcwMwQBs22F-m9q4d7TKaXbJssbq4hZzHnAX74t-cCKY-f1qAukMVHdbrVcdfd8DzhzLATksMOr1lQkvEOpqlEiABReNhh3ZGHc_DtdqY_YdBn' target='_blank'>Oral &amp; Maxillofacial Surgery MSc (Dent Sci)</a> University of Glasgow</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWS9Dw-IwEDkwEEEEEEke_8ACbPs9BhBhc75iv2nLStnhS3sCv6fhvhcLS8RLp8x9B8jhShP8ijDJhFk-9BkJ9FkNQAoJ' target='_bl