	</li>	<li>心血管与医学科学研究院（Institute of Cardiovascular and Medical Sciences）	<ul>		<li>心脏研究（Cardiac Research）</li>		<li>血管学研究（Vascular Research）</li>		<li>代谢病与糖尿病研究（Metabolic Disease &amp; Diabetes Research）</li>		<li>肾研究（Renal Research）</li>		<li>中风研究（Stroke Research）</li>		<li>组学研究（-Omics Research）*(20)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>感染、免疫与炎症研究院（Institute of Infection, Immunity and Inflammation）	<ul>		<li>免疫生物学（Immunobiology）</li>		<li>细菌学（Bacteriology）</li>		<li>寄生虫学（Parasitology）</li>		<li>病毒学（Virology）*(21)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>医学院（School of Medicine）	<ul>		<li>格拉斯哥大学生物医学（Glasgow Biomedicine）</li>		<li>牙医学院研究（Dental School Research）</li>		<li>医学研究（Medical Research）</li>		<li>护理与卫生医疗研究（Nursing and Health Care Research）*(22)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>中国申请者学校背景与学术成绩要求：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ErbpefwUL-Fj7b5GzzzzzzIW_LntJEZFojoj4HelBqI7fpIjfhZlf5NWfqZlf5NWf-d3JPxUIUHqr3EhiG8Stw' target='_blank'>Chinese institutions and entry requirements&nbsp;</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>医学、兽医与生命科学院授课型项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFKokEmsA9JL------hnRtBLNxQSvJVeVeIYupMd5pyJep1T6FzCLcFZ2tXSfbwxGvC9lE0LFTBsNL' target='_blank'>Postgraduate taught programmes</a></li>	<li>医学、兽医与生命科学院PhD项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyf1LSONzWHCAAAAABUqb6WQZYV-tmzqzqk1OoZR_mhtEmbkYBKA1FBOgjptfxsW_Tmv_lQP0epC2LPu2VkL3_lz-MRY10mz-EhiCWgLDM_BhCE_BOXb8ZcoWm46WyUlgwNeKqoegiXlYiXRf' target='_blank'>Research Opportunities</a></li>	<li>奖学金搜索工具：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJ6jL5VUFGwxooooooszkwSXx4AP-VeUeUuWs7w0xO5TkOtqoZr5GA8txGBC5OA8D154ela' target='_blank'>Scholarships and funding</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZE-gkKhq9VW8GGGGGwh9dFkbIi_qHNxNxJaVKNDj5QGS5PGLyYDRxPDPaQGHgQOH-P0kaLVTV8V4ysjTyOwWNFQQxkOrA4cQbC' target='_blank'>Bioinformatics, Polyomics and Systems Biology MSc</a> University of Glasgow</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4AscJMLw